dsDescriptionValue.value:
This submission includes publicly available data extracted in its original form. Please reference the Related Publication listed here for source and citation information

"Zipped file[s] with all awards made in that fiscal year (October 1 - September 30) in JSON format." Files available with awards from 1960 to 2025 by year and Historical awards. "The 'Historical Awards' link contains all awards made prior to 1976. Please note that some data, such as text abstracts, are not available for these older awards." [Quotes from https://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/download.jsp]

fields.value:
This submission includes publicly available data extracted in its original form. Please reference the Related Publication listed here for source and citation information.

National Science Foundation Awards by Year data was downloaded by Jonathan Gilmour on 2025-04-25.

• "In January 2025, NSF converted the downloadable format for all awards from XML to JSON.

• In April 2024, NSF extended Program Element Codes (PECs) from four to six digits. Existing four-digit codes were converted to six-digits by adding a '00'. For example, PEC 4634 and 463400 are the same. Any updates to older awards use the new six-digit codes.

Click on a link below to download a zipped file with all awards made in that fiscal year (October 1 - September 30) in JSON format. View JSON schema.

The "Historical Awards" link contains all awards made prior to 1976. Please note that some data, such as text abstracts, are not available for these older awards." [Quote from https://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/download.jsp]
